text: Laurent Hénart (born 15 October 1968) was a member of the National Assembly of France. He represented the Meurthe-et-Moselle department, and is a member of the Radical Party. ==References== * Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:People from Laxou Category:Politicians from Grand Est Category:Radical Party (France) politicians Category:Union of Democrats and Independents politicians Category:Radical Movement politicians Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Mayors of Nancy, France Category:Sciences Po alumni
